{"tid":422441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯英國律師資格 終極一check","createTime":"2017-10-03T05:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T06:02:17.000Z","uid":28195,"like":100,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"8f7a4c416605ca5a3b7d4bca78c2bd3adfc3a4d5","tid":422441,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:13:22.000Z","msg":"睇返英國律師公會，是有要求Continuing Competence Scheme ，即係註冊成為英國律師係要符合進修要求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.lawsociety.org.uk/support-services/advice/articles/continuing-competence-guidance-faqs/#three\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lawsociety.org.uk%2Fsupport-services%2Fadvice%2Farticles%2Fcontinuing-competence-guidance-faqs%2F%23three&d=hSaw7YAqDoR7w%2BFi8M%2Fsyv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=bb5f1a22\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.lawsociety.org.uk/support-services/advice/articles/continuing-competence-guidance-faqs/#three</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Who must comply with the new continuing competence scheme?</span><br />\n<br />\nFrom 1 November 2016, any solicitor with a practising certificate, wherever in the world they practice and whether or not they are practising English law, is expected to comply with the continuing competence scheme. This includes retired solicitors who maintain a practising certificate, registered European lawyers (RELs) but not registered foreign lawyers (RFLs).<br />\n<br />\n非常懷疑何君堯並沒有comply continuing competence scheme<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打識得check 下？如果無的話，全港香檳應該會沽清呀"},{"pid":"10409718324a69918ffb3e7c358b5192b0587a17","tid":422441,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"有無律師巴絲知道？"},{"pid":"e13ee5fbb0733c25cbd411880c6c5cfd82d0aed9","tid":422441,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b025e47a274cf48370050acdd06c8db7380daec","tid":422441,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daba055afe9e8b22c5aaf68063b8fff805e0b4cd","tid":422441,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:27:36.000Z","msg":"古巴英聯邦"},{"pid":"0fb7f2dabac14e7a5f81f1ddcc3cfa68c1819e15","tid":422441,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:29:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"222106bf881c71f7616e3fb7823fdf2162c2c7b8","tid":422441,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:29:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇返英國律師公會，是有要求Continuing Competence Scheme ，即係註冊成為英國律師係要符合進修要求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.lawsociety.org.uk/support-services/advice/articles/continuing-competence-guidance-faqs/#three\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lawsociety.org.uk%2Fsupport-services%2Fadvice%2Farticles%2Fcontinuing-competence-guidance-faqs%2F%23three&d=hSaw7YAqDoR7w%2BFi8M%2Fsyv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=bb5f1a22\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.lawsociety.org.uk/support-services/advice/articles/continuing-competence-guidance-faqs/#three</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Who must comply with the new continuing competence scheme?</span><br />\n<br />\nFrom 1 November 2016, <span style=\"color: red;\">any solicitor with a practising certificate</span>, wherever in the world they practice and whether or not they are practising English law, is expected to comply with the continuing competence scheme. This includes retired solicitors who maintain a practising certificate, registered European lawyers (RELs) but not registered foreign lawyers (RFLs).<br />\n<br />\n非常懷疑何君堯並沒有comply continuing competence scheme<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打識得check 下？如果無的話，全港香檳應該會沽清呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nany solicitor with a practising certificate<br />\n<br />\n佢自己都認冇執業喎"},{"pid":"4e28